summary: 35 & Ticking (also known as Russ Parr's 35 & Ticking or 35 and Ticking) is an American romantic comedy film written and directed by Russ Parr.The film stars a mostly African American ensemble cast featuring Meagan Good, Nicole Ari Parker, Tamala Jones, Kevin Hart, Kym Whitley, Darius McCrary, Dondre Whitfield, Mike Epps, Luenell, Clifton Powell, Jill Marie Jones, Wendy Raquel Robinson, and Keith Robinson. The film had its limited release in theaters on May 20, 2011.
cast:
Nicole Ari Parker as Zenobia
Keith Robinson as Phil
Tamala Jones as Victoria
Kevin Hart as Cleavon
Meagan Good as Falinda
Jill Marie Jones as Coco
Kym Whitley as Shavelle
Luenell as Donya
Darius McCrary as Nick West
Dondre Whitfield as Austin
Mike Epps as Harold
Wendy Raquel Robinson as Calise
Clifton Powell as Zane
Aaron D. Spears as Officer Jones
Angelique Bates as Gangsta Girl
Skoti Collins as Officer Bade
